 
<p>

US citizens: call on the Senate to <a href="https://actionnetwork.org/forms/sign-the-petition-to-senate-democrats-abolish-blue-slips">abolish "blue slips" for blocking
    judicial nominations</a>.
<p>
This is the system whereby judges from a state can veto appointment
of judges in that state.

